<anchor id="metric_8h_1metrics_builder"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>Metrics are send cyclically via LTE to the MQTT broker. the metrics builder is responsible to prepare the metrics JSON string, which contains all provided metrics data and to clear it after transmission. See also message sequence charts <ref refid="_m_s_c_1SectionMetrics" kindref="member">Metrics</ref>.</para>
</simplesect>
